HEADWORD: hickie
<hw>hick"ie</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Elec.)</fld> <def>A device used to adapt a lighting fixture for
mounting in an outlet box, or on a pipe.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A red mark on the skin, caused by a passionate,
sucking kiss at that location.</def> <mark>[slang]</mark> ⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>a <er>doohickey</er>.</def>
<mark>[informal]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hickory</ent>⟦br⟧
